title: The Eagles Live In New Zealand 1995
description: The Eagles Live in New Zealand 1995. Don Henley, Glen Frey, Timothy B.Schimdt, Joe Walsh, Don Felder. Video Quality 7 The audio is what intrigued me. Myself being a guitar player. I found the audio mix tended to favor the guitars of Walsh and Felder. So that being said there is no other video like it anywhere else. You'll hear guitar blends of their songs like no other. Enjoy
